window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Destruction looms on the horizon.</b></p> <p>As she settles into life in Paragon City as a new heroine, Lilith is slowly adapting to how her life has changed. One of those changes is an invitation to speak at a renowned superhero convention in Las Vegas.</p> <p>Hopeful that this will be a chance to turn her reputation around, Lilith chooses to attend with Gina and Rachel. Unfortunately for Lilith, Destruction Corps hasn’t forgotten its humiliation, and she’s walking into a trap. One that could end the lives of thousands if she and the heroes don’t act quickly enough.</p>"; 
